OL,4,Cwound that has been open for 26 years'
OL,6,FThe sister of a young Spanish woman
OL,7,Fkilled in the Omagh bombing has
OL,8,Fdescribed a public inquiry into the
OL,9,Fatrocity as "allowing us to close a
OL,10,Fwound that has been open for 26 years".
OL,12,FRocio Abad Ramos, 23, from Madrid was
OL,13,Famong 29 people, including a woman
OL,14,Fpregnant with twins, who were killed
OL,15,Fin the dissident republican bomb
OL,16,Fattack in the Co Tyrone town in 1998.
OL,26,@qD@MOUrD@fO]
