OL,6,FShe had been involved in an exchange
OL,7,Ftrip with young Spanish children to
OL,8,FBuncrana in Co Donegal. They had been
OL,9,Fvisiting Omagh on August 15 when the
OL,10,Fbomb exploded.
OL,12,FHer sister Paloma Abad Ramos gave
OL,13,Fevidence to the Omagh Bombing Inquiry
OL,14,Fon Tuesday as it started commemorative
OL,15,Fhearings focusing on the victims and
OL,16,Fthose affected.
