OL,3,COmagh inquiry 'allowing us to close
OL,4,Cwound that has been open for 26 years'
OL,6,FSpeaking through a translator, Ms
OL,7,FRamos also told the inquiry she hoped
OL,8,Fit will uncover the truth of what
OL,9,Fhappened, saying she felt the news in
OL,10,FSpain at the time had been
OL,11,F"restricted".
OL,13,FShe thanked those behind the inquiry,
OL,14,Fsaying: "This is the only support that
OL,15,Fwe've had for many many years".
OL,17,FCompleting her evidence, she said: "I
OL,18,Fon behalf of my family want to thank
OL,19,Fyou, the inquiry, for this opportunity
OL,20,Fbecause you are allowing us to close a
OL,21,Fwound that has been open for 26 years".
