OL,6,FWhile Ms Ramos's evidence was at times
OL,7,Femotional, she also recalled how her
OL,8,Fsister, who had been to Ireland five
OL,9,Ftimes, had initially not been
OL,10,Fimpressed with the local food,
OL,11,Fcomplaining about seeing butter and
OL,12,Fpeas everywhere.
OL,14,FBut she said she grew to enjoy Irish
OL,15,Ffood, even exchanging recipes with
OL,16,Fthose she had befriended in Donegal.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
