OL,6,FHaving travelled from Spain to give
OL,7,Fevidence at the inquiry at the Strule
OL,8,FArts Centre in Omagh, Ms Ramos said
OL,9,Fshe had thought about how hard it
OL,10,Fwould be to go to Omagh where her
OL,11,Fsister had died.
OL,13,FBut she said in fact it had been
OL,14,Fdifficult to be at the airport because
OL,15,Fthat was the last place she had seen
OL,16,Fher alive.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
