OL,6,FIn her statement to the inquiry she
OL,7,Fsaid when her parents left her sister
OL,8,Fat the airport, she was so excited to
OL,9,Fbe going on the trip, and having just
OL,10,Ffinished her studies she had a world
OL,11,Fof possibilities ahead of her.
OL,13,F"As our parents hugged and said
OL,14,Fgoodbye to Rocio, little did they know
OL,15,Fthat was to be the last time they
OL,16,Fwould see their daughter alive," the
OL,17,Finquiry heard she said in her
OL,18,Fstatement.
