OL,6,FAsked about that during the hearing,
OL,7,FMs Ramos said: "I was thinking it
OL,8,Fwould be very, very difficult to walk
OL,9,Falong the street where the bomb had
OL,10,Fexploded, well this happened to us at
OL,11,Fthe airport, the airport was the last
OL,12,Fplace we saw Rocio alive."
OL,14,FBack in August 1998, she arrived home
OL,15,Ffrom a holiday to learn what had
OL,16,Fhappened to her sister, and followed
OL,17,Fher parents to Belfast, on a military
OL,18,Fplane with the families of other
OL,19,FSpanish citizens who lost their lives
OL,20,For were injured.
OL,26,@oD@POUtD@ZO]
