OL,6,F"Imagine a military plan with no
OL,7,Fseats, seated on a net with 20 more
OL,8,Fpeople, family members of wounded and
OL,9,Fvictims, it was a very tense
OL,10,Fsituation," she told the inquiry.
OL,12,FShe paid tribute to being sheltered
OL,13,Ffrom seeing the bomb scene. She also
OL,14,Ftold the inquiry she wanted to thank
OL,15,Fthose who recovered her sister's
OL,16,Fremains, describing going to the
OL,17,Fmorgue as a "moment I will never
OL,18,Fforget in my life".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]yD@MOUzD@RO]
