OL,6,FThey returned to Madrid on a military
OL,7,Fplane, with two coffins, Rocio's, as
OL,8,Fwell as that of 12-year-old Fernando
OL,9,FBlasco Baselga who was also killed in
OL,10,Fthe bomb.
OL,12,FShe described hugging her sister's
OL,13,Fcoffin on the flight back.
OL,15,FOn their return to Madrid, the two
OL,16,Fcoffins were covered with Spanish
OL,17,Fflags and given a military parade, and
OL,18,Flater a state funeral which she
OL,19,Fcompared to a Champions League final
OL,20,Fwith crowds of people in attendance,
OL,21,Fincluding the King's daughter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
