OL,6,F"I was in shock, just three days
OL,7,Fbefore we learned that our sister had
OL,8,Fbeen killed in a terrorist bombing in
OL,9,FIreland, it was mind-blowing and we
OL,10,Fwere not able to cope with this," she
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"We were directed to (the) funeral
OL,14,Fparlour, it was like the final of the
OL,15,FChampions League because there were
OL,16,Fso, so many people, our grief was made
OL,17,Fpublic ... we were not left in peace."
OL,19,FMs Ramos summed her sister up as an
OL,20,Fextrovert, and a "very special person"
OL,21,Fwho had a love of Ireland.
